'''Ian Hughes''' (born 13 March 1962) is a former professional [[rugby league]] [[football]]er of the 1980s, '90s and 2000s who at club level has played for [[Wakefield Trinity Wildcats|Wakefield Trinity]], [[Sheffield Eagles]], and [[Keighley Cougars]], playing {{rlp|SR}}, i.e. number 11 or 12.<ref name="Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org">{{cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/players/Ian_Hughes/summary.html|title=Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org|publisher=rugbyleagueproject.org|date=2010-12-31|accessdate=2011-01-01}}</ref>

